OL,3,CNurses begin tribunal proceedings
OL,4,Cagainst NHS trust over trans colleague
OL,6,FAn employment tribunal is starting for
OL,7,Fa group of nurses who are challenging
OL,8,Ftheir health trust over its policy of
OL,9,Fallowing a trans colleague to use the
OL,10,Ffemale changing rooms at work.
OL,12,FThe seven nurses are taking action
OL,13,Fagainst County Durham and Darlington
OL,14,FNHS Foundation Trust after a
OL,15,Fcolleague, Rose Henderson, who was
OL,16,Fborn male but who identifies as a
OL,17,Fwoman, was allowed to use the women's
OL,18,Fchanging facilities at Darlington
OL,19,FMemorial Hospital.
