OL,4,Cagainst NHS trust over trans colleague
OL,6,FThe trust says it is committed to
OL,7,Fproviding environments that are "safe,
OL,8,Frespectful and inclusive" for patients
OL,9,Fand staff.
OL,11,FThe nurses work in the day surgery
OL,12,Funit and have to travel to the
OL,13,Fhospital in their own clothes and
OL,14,Fchange into their uniforms once they
OL,15,Farrive.
OL,17,FIf they leave the hospital for a
OL,18,Fbreak, they must change out of their
OL,19,Funiforms.
