OL,3,CNurses begin tribunal proceedings
OL,4,Cagainst NHS trust over trans colleague
OL,6,FThe nurses will claim that NHS
OL,7,Fguidance stated that women who
OL,8,Fobjected to sharing changing
OL,9,Ffacilities with trans colleagues "will
OL,10,Fnot be tolerated" and that they must
OL,11,Ffind somewhere else to change.
OL,13,FThey claim that Rose Henderson has a
OL,14,Fgirlfriend and that the couple hoped
OL,15,Fto conceive a child, implying that "he
OL,16,Fis a sexually active biological male".
