OL,3,CNurses begin tribunal proceedings
OL,4,Cagainst NHS trust over trans colleague
OL,6,FIn their particulars of claim
OL,7,Fdocument, the nurses say that the
OL,8,Fhealth trust "permits any member of
OL,9,Fstaff (regardless of sex and
OL,10,Fregardless of gender reassignment) to
OL,11,Fchoose their 'gender identity' and to
OL,12,Faccess a single-sex changing room on
OL,13,Fthat basis".
OL,15,FTheir document claims that since
OL,16,FAugust 2023, Rose Henderson has used
OL,17,Fthe female changing area and has
OL,18,Fstared at female colleagues "in
OL,19,Fparticular their breast area" as they
OL,20,Fget changed.
