OL,3,CNurses begin tribunal proceedings
OL,4,Cagainst NHS trust over trans colleague
OL,6,FOne of the claimants said that Rose
OL,7,FHenderson repeatedly asked: "Are you
OL,8,Fnot getting changed yet?"
OL,10,FThe nurses claim they have suffered
OL,11,Fanxiety and distress, that they feel
OL,12,Funsafe at work and "that their privacy
OL,13,Fand dignity have been violated".
OL,15,FThe hearing, expected to take more
OL,16,Fthan three weeks, will be held at
OL,17,FNewcastle Tribunal Centre.
